metadata.name: Sculptura #1: Anatomy of the Infamous
metadata.description:
1/1 minted on SCULPTURA by Mad Monk, 2022

First mint of the smart contract.. 

Sculptura is an AI assisted sculpture and installation concept by Mad Monk. It is a maze of experimentation with various forms and influences. Mostly about form, color and visual experimentation, the concept harbors its own surprises. Sculptura is minted on its own Manifold powered smart contract as well as on the platforms Mad Monk creates on.
